import React from "react";

  FooterLinksWrapper,
  FooterLinksItems,
  FooterLink,
} from "./FooterElements";

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <FooterLinksContainer>
      <FooterLinksWrapper>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Account and Billing</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Plans and Pricing</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">FAQ</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Help Center</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Privacy</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Terms of Use</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
      </FooterLinksWrapper>
      <SocialMedia>
        <SocialMediaWrap>
          <SocialLogo to="/">
            <SocialIcon />
            MOVIEFLIX
          </SocialLogo>
          <WebsiteRights>MOVIE</WebsiteRights>
        </SocialMediaWrap>
      </SocialMedia>
    </FooterLinksContainer>
  );
};

export default Footer;
